      <title>欧洲央行金多斯认为工资增长放缓，但对利率持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/ecb-s-guindos-sees-wage-growth-slowing-but-is-cagey-on-rate-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副行长路易斯·德金多斯表示，欧元区工资增长正在放缓，但由于不确定性增加，欧洲央行无法承诺降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/ecb-s-guindos-sees-wage-growth-slowing-but-is-cagey-on-rate-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
