      <title>红海扰乱正在分裂全球液化天然气贸易的地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/red-sea-disruptions-are-splitting-global-lng-trade-into-regions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四个月前，一艘液化天然气油轮通过了红海南端分隔阿拉伯半岛和非洲的狭窄海峡，这证明了那里的暴力袭击如何颠覆了全球能源贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/red-sea-disruptions-are-splitting-global-lng-trade-into-regions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
